<text><body>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0466c" xml:id="T21.1315.0466c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0466c01" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0466c02" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0466c03" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><cb:docNumber>No. 1315</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0466c04" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0466011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，【甲】三十帖策子第二十六</note>施諸餓鬼飲食及水法<note place="inline">并手印</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0466c05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0466c06" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0466012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔特進…三藏〕十二字－【甲】</note><note n="0466012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（特進…三藏）十二字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="12" n="0466012"><lem wit="【大】">特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>沙門
<lb n="0466c07" ed="T"/>大廣智不空<note n="0466013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">奉詔＝三藏【甲】</note><note n="0466013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奉詔【大】，三藏【甲】</note><app n="0466013"><lem wit="【大】">奉　詔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">三藏</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0466c08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0466c0801">先出眾生食。事須如法。周匝種種皆著並
<lb n="0466c09" ed="T"/>須淨好。或一分或少許或一器。皆須安淨銅
<lb n="0466c10" ed="T"/>器中如法。如無銅器白瓷亦得。如無瓷器可
<lb n="0466c11" ed="T"/>用漆器。其飲食須和清水。面向東立坐亦得
<lb n="0466c12" ed="T"/>作法。</p>
<lb n="0466c13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0466c1301">夫欲施一切餓鬼飲食者。先須發廣大心普
<lb n="0466c14" ed="T"/>請餓鬼。<note n="0466014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">先＋（請）【甲】</note><note n="0466014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">先【大】，先請【甲】</note><app n="0466014"><lem wit="【大】">先</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">先請</rdg></app>誦此偈至<note n="0466015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔心〕－【甲】</note><note n="0466015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0466015"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>一遍。然<note n="0466016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔後〕－【甲】</note><note n="0466016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">後【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0466016"><lem wit="【大】">後</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>作<note n="0466017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔召〕－【甲】</note><note n="0466017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">召【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0466017"><lem wit="【大】">召</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0466c15" ed="T"/>請法。所獲福利果報不可校量。</p>
<lb n="0466c16" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0466c1601"><l>比丘比丘尼<note place="inline">某甲</note>發心奉持</l><l>一器淨食</l>
<lb n="0466c17" ed="T"/><l>普施十方</l><l>窮盡虛空</l><l>周遍法界</l>
<lb n="0466c18" ed="T"/><l>微塵剎中</l><l>所有國土</l><l>一切餓鬼</l>
<lb n="0466c19" ed="T"/><l>先亡久遠</l><l>山川地主</l><l>乃至曠野</l>
<lb n="0466c20" ed="T"/><l>諸鬼神等</l><l>請來集此</l><l>我今悲愍</l>
<lb n="0466c21" ed="T"/><l>普施汝食</l><l>願汝各各</l><l>受我此食</l>
<lb n="0466c22" ed="T"/><l>轉將供養</l><l>盡虛空界</l><l>以佛及聖</l>
<lb n="0466c23" ed="T"/><l>一切有情</l><l>汝與有情</l><l>普皆飽滿</l>
<lb n="0466c24" ed="T"/><l>亦願汝身</l><l>乘此呪食</l><l>離苦解脫</l>
<lb n="0466c25" ed="T"/><l>生天受樂</l><l>十方淨土</l><l>隨意遊往</l>
<lb n="0466c26" ed="T"/><l>發菩提心</l><l>行菩提道</l><l>當來作佛</l>
<lb n="0466c27" ed="T"/><l>永莫退轉</l><l>前得道者</l><l>誓相度脫</l>
<lb n="0466c28" ed="T"/><l>又願汝等</l><l>晝夜恒常</l><l>擁護於我</l>
<lb n="0466c29" ed="T"/><l>滿我所願</l><l>願施此食</l><l>所生功德</l>
<pb n="0467a" xml:id="T21.1315.0467a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0467a01" ed="T"/><l>普將廻施</l><l>法界有情</l><l>與諸有情</l>
<lb n="0467a02" ed="T"/><l>平等共有</l><l>共諸有情</l><l>同將此福</l>
<lb n="0467a03" ed="T"/><l>盡將迴向</l><l>真如法界</l><l>無上菩提</l>
<lb n="0467a04" ed="T"/><l>一切智智</l><l>願速成佛</l><l>勿招餘果</l>
<lb n="0467a05" ed="T"/><l>願<note n="0467001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">乘＝我【甲】</note><note n="0467001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乘【大】，我【甲】</note><app n="0467001"><lem wit="【大】">乘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">我</rdg></app>此法</l><l>疾得成佛</l></lg>
<lb n="0467a06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0467a0601">合掌當心誦此偈。以印作召請　開喉印　以
<lb n="0467a07" ed="T"/>右手大指與中指。面相捻。餘三指相去。微作
<lb n="0467a08" ed="T"/>曲勢即是。名普集印　呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0467a09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0467a0901" cb:type="dharani"><note n="0467002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">甲本梵字總無之</note><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5A9"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">曩</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5ED"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">謨＝慕【甲】</note><note n="0467003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謨【大】，慕【甲】</note><app n="0467003"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">慕</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5DE"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">步</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5B9"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>布</cb:zi><cb:sg><note n="0467004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔入〕－【甲】＊</note><note n="0467004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入【大】＊，〔－〕【甲】＊</note><app n="0467004"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A640"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">哩＝唎【甲】＊</note><note n="0467005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">哩【大】＊，唎【甲】＊</note><app n="0467005"><lem wit="【大】">哩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唎</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A440"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">迦</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A640"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><app type="star" corresp="#0467005"><lem wit="【大】">哩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唎</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A557"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">多＝哆【甲】＊</note><note n="0467006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多【大】＊，哆【甲】＊</note><app n="0467006"><lem wit="【大】">多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">哆</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A640"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><app type="star" corresp="#0467005"><lem wit="【大】">哩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唎</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A557"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">怛</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A564"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>他</cb:zi><cb:sg><note n="0467007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【甲】＊</note><note n="0467007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】＊，〔－〕【甲】＊</note><app n="0467007"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt>
<lb n="0467a10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0467a11" ed="T"/><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A458"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蘖＝揭【甲】＊</note><note n="0467008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蘖【大】＊，揭【甲】＊</note><app n="0467008"><lem wit="【大】">蘖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">揭</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A558"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><app type="star" corresp="#0467006"><lem wit="【大】">多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">哆</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5F1"/><g ref="#SD-D9C6"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">也</cb:t></cb:tt></p>
<lb n="0467a12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0467a13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0467a1301">作此印誦此呪一七遍。廣運悲心。願令法界
<lb n="0467a14" ed="T"/>微塵剎中。一切餓鬼悉皆雲集。</p>
<lb n="0467a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0467a1501">又誦開地獄門及咽喉呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0467a16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0467a1601" cb:type="dharani"><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-DA42"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">唵</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5DE"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">步</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5B9"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>布</cb:zi><cb:sg><app type="star" corresp="#0467004"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A55D"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">帝＝諦【甲】＊</note><note n="0467009" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->帝【大】＊，諦【甲】＊</note><app n="0467009"><lem wit="【大】">帝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">諦</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A640"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><app type="star" corresp="#0467005"><lem wit="【大】">哩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唎</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A440"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">迦</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A557"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">多</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A640"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><app type="star" corresp="#0467005"><lem wit="【大】">哩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唎</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A557"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">怛</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A564"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">他</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A458"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><app type="star" corresp="#0467008"><lem wit="【大】">蘖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">揭</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt>
<lb n="0467a17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0467a18" ed="T"/><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A558"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi><app type="star" corresp="#0467006"><lem wit="【大】">多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">哆</rdg></app></cb:zi><cb:sg><app type="star" corresp="#0467007"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5F1"/><g ref="#SD-D9C6"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">也</cb:t></cb:tt></p>
<lb n="0467a19" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0467a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0467a2001">誦此呪時。以左手執持食器。以右手作前召
<lb n="0467a21" ed="T"/>請印。唯改一誦呪一彈指。以大指與中指頭
<lb n="0467a22" ed="T"/>相捻。彈指作聲即是。餘三指開稍微曲此名
<lb n="0467a23" ed="T"/>破地獄門及開咽喉印。爾時如來。即說無量
<lb n="0467a24" ed="T"/>威德自在光明勝妙之力加持飲食陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0467a25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0467a2501" cb:type="dharani"><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5A9"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">曩</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5F0"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">莫＝慕【甲】＊</note><note n="0467010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莫【大】＊，慕【甲】＊</note><app n="0467010"><lem wit="【大】">莫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">慕</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A67A"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">薩</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-B7A3"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚩＝婆【甲】</note><note n="0467011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚩【大】，婆【甲】</note><app n="0467011"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">婆</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A557"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">怛</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A564"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">他＋（去）夾註【甲】＊</note><note n="0467012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">他【大】＊，他(去)【甲】＊</note><app n="0467012"><lem wit="【大】">他</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">他<note place="inline">去</note></rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A458"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">蘖</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A558"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">多嚩嚕吉帝＝哆引一縛路枳帝二【甲】</note><note n="0467013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多嚩嚕吉帝【大】，哆引一縛路枳帝二【甲】</note>多</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A656"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">嚩</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A652"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">嚕</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A442"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">吉</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A55D"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">帝</cb:t></cb:tt>
<lb n="0467a26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0467a27" ed="T"/><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-DA42"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唵＋（跋囉上跋囉三）【甲】</note><note n="0467014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唵【大】，唵跋囉上跋囉三【甲】</note><app n="0467014"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唵跋囉上跋囉三</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A6A6"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">三</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5D9"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婆羅＝跋囉【甲】</note><note n="0467015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">娑羅【大】，跋囉【甲】</note>娑</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5FD"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">羅</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A6A6"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">三</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5D9"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婆羅＝跋囉四【甲】</note><note n="0467016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婆羅【大】，跋囉四【甲】</note>婆</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5FD"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">羅</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-DA74"/><g ref="#SD-D9C6"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>吽</cb:zi><cb:sg><note n="0467017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＝虎叫【甲】</note><note n="0467017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，虎叫【甲】</note><app n="0467017"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">虎叫</rdg></app></cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt></p>
<lb n="0467a28" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0467a29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0467a2901">誦此呪一七遍。一切餓鬼<note n="0467018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">各＋（各）【甲】</note><note n="0467018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">各【大】，各各【甲】</note><app n="0467018"><lem wit="【大】">各</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">各各</rdg></app>皆得摩伽陀國
<pb n="0467b" xml:id="T21.1315.0467b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0467b01" ed="T"/>所用之斗<note n="0467019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔七〕－【甲】</note><note n="0467019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">七【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0467019"><lem wit="【大】">七</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>七<note n="0467020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">斛＝斗【甲】</note><note n="0467020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斛【大】，斗【甲】</note><app n="0467020"><lem wit="【大】">斛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">斗</rdg></app>之食。食已皆得生天或
<lb n="0467b02" ed="T"/>生淨土。能令行者業障消除增益壽命。現世
<lb n="0467b03" ed="T"/>獲<note n="0467021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無量無邊福＝福無量無邊【甲】</note><note n="0467021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無量無邊福【大】，福無量無邊【甲】</note><app n="0467021"><lem wit="【大】">無量無邊福</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">福無量無邊</rdg></app>。況當來世。<note n="0467022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔即〕－【甲】</note><note n="0467022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0467022"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>作手印誦此
<lb n="0467b04" ed="T"/><note n="0467023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔真言〕－【甲】＊</note><note n="0467023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">真言【大】＊，〔－〕【甲】＊</note><app n="0467023"><lem wit="【大】">真言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>加持飲食。以右手大指。摩中指甲三兩
<lb n="0467b05" ed="T"/>遍。三指直<note n="0467024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔立〕－【甲】</note><note n="0467024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">立【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0467024"><lem wit="【大】">立</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>之。又以大指捻頭指。彈指作
<lb n="0467b06" ed="T"/>聲。一誦呪一彈指即是。</p>
<lb n="0467b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0467b0701">又誦蒙甘露法味<app type="star" corresp="#0467023"><lem wit="【大】">真言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。作施無畏印。以右手
<lb n="0467b08" ed="T"/>竪臂。展五指直上即是。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0467b09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0467b0901" cb:type="dharani"><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5A9"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">曩</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5F0"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><app type="star" corresp="#0467010"><lem wit="【大】">莫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">慕</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-E0BC"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蘇＋（上）夾註【甲】</note><note n="0467025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蘇【大】，蘇(上)【甲】</note><app n="0467025"><lem wit="【大】">蘇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">蘇<note place="inline">上</note></rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A643"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">嚕</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5B5"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">頗也＝播也二合去一【甲】</note><note n="0467026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頗也【大】，播也二合去一【甲】</note>頗</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5F1"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">也</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A557"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">怛</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A564"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><app type="star" corresp="#0467012"><lem wit="【大】">他</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">他<note place="inline">去</note></rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A458"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">蘖</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A558"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><app type="star" corresp="#0467006"><lem wit="【大】">多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">哆</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5F1"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">也＋（二）夾註【甲】</note><note n="0467027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也【大】，也(二)【甲】</note><app n="0467027"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">也<note place="inline">二</note></rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A557"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">怛</cb:t></cb:tt>
<lb n="0467b10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0467b11" ed="T"/><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A7EF"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">儞也他唵蘇＝姪嬭也反他去三唵四蘇二合【甲】</note><note n="0467028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">儞也他唵蘇【大】，姪嬭也反他去三唵四蘇二合【甲】</note>儞也</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A564"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">他</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-DA42"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">唵</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-AB7A"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">蘇嚕</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-AB7A"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蘇嚕＝蘇上嚕五【甲】</note><note n="0467029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蘇嚕【大】，蘇上嚕五【甲】</note><app n="0467029"><lem wit="【大】">蘇嚕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">蘇上嚕五</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-DA44"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0467030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鉢＝跋【甲】＊</note><note n="0467030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鉢【大】＊，跋【甲】＊</note><app n="0467030"><lem wit="【大】">鉢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">跋</rdg></app>羅</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-AB7A"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">蘇<note n="0467031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚕＋（六）夾註【甲】</note><note n="0467031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚕【大】，嚕(六)【甲】</note><app n="0467031"><lem wit="【大】">嚕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">嚕<note place="inline">六</note></rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-DA44"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><app type="star" corresp="#0467030"><lem wit="【大】">鉢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">跋</rdg></app>羅</cb:t></cb:tt>
<lb n="0467b12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0467b13" ed="T"/><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-AB7A"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">蘇<note n="0467032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚕＋（七）夾註【甲】</note><note n="0467032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚕【大】，嚕(七)【甲】</note><app n="0467032"><lem wit="【大】">嚕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">嚕<note place="inline">七</note></rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-DA49"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>娑<note n="0467033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚩＝縛【甲】</note><note n="0467033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚩【大】，縛【甲】</note><app n="0467033"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app></cb:zi><cb:sg>二合</cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A6A9"/><g ref="#SD-D9C6"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi><note n="0467034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">賀＝訶【甲】</note><note n="0467034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賀【大】，訶【甲】</note><app n="0467034"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">訶</rdg></app></cb:zi><cb:sg><app type="star" corresp="#0467007"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt></p>
<lb n="0467b14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0467b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0467b1501">作前施無畏印。誦此<note n="0467035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔呪〕－ヵ【原】</note><note n="0467035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呪【大】，〔－〕【考偽-原】</note><app n="0467035"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">呪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>施甘露真言一七遍。
<lb n="0467b16" ed="T"/>能令飲食及水。變成無量乳及甘露。能開一
<lb n="0467b17" ed="T"/>切餓鬼咽喉。能令飲食廣得增多平等得<note n="0467036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔喫〕－【甲】</note><note n="0467036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喫【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0467036"><lem wit="【大】">喫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0467b18" ed="T"/>也。</p>
<lb n="0467b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0467b1901">次作毘盧遮那一字心水輪觀真言<note n="0467037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔印〕－【甲】</note><note n="0467037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0467037"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。先想
<lb n="0467b20" ed="T"/>此<term xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-E1AF"/></term>鑁字<note n="0467038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">於＝以【甲】</note><note n="0467038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於【大】，以【甲】</note><app n="0467038"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">以</rdg></app>右手心中。猶如乳色。變為<note n="0467039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔八〕－【甲】</note><note n="0467039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0467039"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0467b21" ed="T"/>功德海。流出一切甘露醍醐。即引手臨食器
<lb n="0467b22" ed="T"/>上<note n="0467040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔呪曰〕－ヵ【原】</note><note n="0467040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呪曰【大】，〔－〕【考偽-原】</note><app n="0467040"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">呪<note n="0467041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔曰誦〕－【甲】</note><note n="0467041" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: a-->曰誦【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note>曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。誦此<term xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-E1AF"/></term><note n="0467042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔鑁〕－【甲】</note><note n="0467042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鑁【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0467042"><lem wit="【大】">鑁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>字一七遍。即展開五
<lb n="0467b23" ed="T"/>指。向下臨食器中。觀想乳等從字中流出。猶
<lb n="0467b24" ed="T"/>如日月乳海。一切鬼等皆得飽滿無有乏少。
<lb n="0467b25" ed="T"/>此名普施一切餓鬼印真言曰。</p>
